Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,O..i !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Minatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thiệt là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhỏ này cũng trốn việc sao kà?
